Tammin Sursok https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tammin_Sursok 0 Tammin Pamela Sursok (born 19 August 1983) is a South African-born Australian actress and singer. She is known for her roles on television as Dani Sutherland on Home and Away, Colleen Carlton on The Young and the Restless, and Jenna Marshall on Pretty Little Liars.
